team.description: Google Developers' Group Springfield is a place for local developers specifically interested in Google products and APIs to meet and create, collaborate, and learn together. We aim to host a variety of technical activities - from just a few people getting together to watch our latest videos, to large gatherings with demos and tech talks, to hackathons. Our meetings are always free and open to the general public.
